data.description: Popular 4 Bedroom Aubrey Plan by Robertson Construction in Brooke Hills! Main level is open with hardwood floors in the Kitchen and Dining. Kitchen has a pantry and granite tops. Covered Deck right off the Kitchen/Dining for your outdoor living enjoyment. Living Room has a gas fireplace with decorative trim. Master is on it's own wing, separate from two additional beds on the main level. Finished basement features a bedroom, full bath, and living area. Staley High School.
